articles.title: Brendan Fraser and Rachel Weisz in talks to star in fourth Mummy movie
articles.content: In the original film series, Fraser played American adventurer and treasure hunter Rick O'Connell, while Weisz played Cairo-based English librarian and aspiring Egyptologist Evelyn Carnahan. Together with Evelyn's brother Jonathan, played by John Hannah, they visit an ancient Egyptian city and accidentally awaken a mummy named Imhotep.
